data.description: This delightful single-story home, nestled on a tranquil dead-end street, showcases three bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and a single-car garage. Embraced by a generous fenced yard equipped with a sprinkler system, this charming residence is ideally positioned in the heart of Jupiter. Recent updates include a new roof in 2018, an upgraded HVAC system in 2019, and modern appliances. The third bedroom currently functions as a den but can effortlessly be transformed into a bedroom. Additionally, residents enjoy the convenience of extra parking available at the street's end.
